metadata.name: Rooted
metadata.description:
"They tried to bury us, but they did not know we were seeds" -  Dinos Christianopoulos

"Rooted" is about life, death and rebirth. It also depicts our dualistic relationship with nature: our attempts to stay grounded, while putting pressure on our environment. 
All flowers in this artwork were hand-picked, pressed, and digitalised. 

Digital pressed flower collage  
3600px X 3600px  
300 DBI

This artwork is authentic and was created by dodsicle; the purchase of the NFT is a purchase of the asset, not of the copyright.
